we've isolated them,

20:01.040 --> 20:02.109
we need to test them
individually.

20:02.120 --> 20:03.030
Yeah, on it.

20:03.040 --> 20:04.450
[fragments playing]

20:04.460 --> 20:06.951
I could listen
In real tIme,

20:06.960 --> 20:08.746
while you monitor each one.

20:08.750 --> 20:10.160
What? Is that safe?

20:11.540 --> 20:14.077
Ben is sure?

20:14.080 --> 20:18.073
If we want answers,
we have to try.

20:28.120 --> 20:29.701
-[light buzzing]
-Must be the circuit breaker.

20:29.710 --> 20:31.280
I'm sorry, Maddie.

20:31.290 --> 20:33.531
-I wouldn't have asked you--
-It's okay.

20:33.540 --> 20:35.747
It's, uh, right here.

20:38.290 --> 20:40.326
So... how are things?

20:40.330 --> 20:41.490
[breaker clicks]

20:42.540 --> 20:43.871
Notgood.

20:43.880 --> 20:46.246
I think all this wiring
might be shot.

20:46.250 --> 20:49.287
No. I meant how are you?

20:49.290 --> 20:52.077
How's Ben?
How's your other friend Ryn?

20:52.080 --> 20:53.570
We're fine, Mom.

20:53.580 --> 20:54.990
You don't have to keep me
in the dark, Maddie.

20:55.000 --> 20:56.956
I'm not that old-fashioned.

20:56.960 --> 20:59.667
People have all kinds
of relationships these days.

20:59.670 --> 21:03.162
I just want to make sure
that yours is healthy.

21:03.170 --> 21:05.035
That looks dangerous.

21:05.040 --> 21:06.371
Not worth you getting hurt.
I'll call the electrician.

21:07.380 --> 21:08.369
Maddie, just leave it.

21:08.380 --> 21:09.745
No! I can fix it!

21:11.040 --> 21:12.200
What a piece of crap.

21:15.080 --> 21:16.820
-Maddie, just--
-Leave me alone!

21:16.830 --> 21:18.115
Aah!

21:21.250 --> 21:22.239
What's gotten into you?

21:23.290 --> 21:25.167
Something's wrong.

21:25.170 --> 21:26.785
Talk to me.

21:28.880 --> 21:30.279
I have to go.

21:30.290 --> 21:31.780
[screwdriver clatters]

21:34.670 --> 21:35.989
Maddie!

21:44.790 --> 21:47.076
Ben and Maddie
are very close to you.

21:47.080 --> 21:49.708
Very protective of you.

21:49.710 --> 21:51.871
Does your song have
anything to do with that?

21:51.880 --> 21:54.280
Not just song.

21:54.290 --> 21:56.281
With Ben and Maddie,
it is more.

21:56.290 --> 21:57.416
More?

21:57.420 --> 22:00.878
Yes. Ryn loves
Ben and Maddie.

22:02.420 --> 22:05.071
Ryn makes love
with Ben and Maddie.

22:14.170 --> 22:15.205
