Ready?

22:15.210 --> 22:18.111
Yeah. Let's do this.

22:18.120 --> 22:19.496
Here we go.

22:19.500 --> 22:20.819
The song in full.

22:20.830 --> 22:22.616
All frequencies.

22:22.620 --> 22:27.375
[Siren song playing]

22:35.960 --> 22:38.201
[monitors beeping]

22:42.620 --> 22:44.372
My song does this?

22:44.380 --> 22:48.282
[Siren song continuing]

22:50.120 --> 22:51.667
Whoa.

22:51.670 --> 22:53.376
[song continuing]

22:53.380 --> 22:55.371
