[Nicole] What?

23:12.620 --> 23:16.454
Most humans can hear
frequencies between
20 hertz and 20,000.

23:16.460 --> 23:18.109
Sea creatures,
like some dolphins,

23:18.120 --> 23:20.532
can hear frequencies
up to 100,000 hertz,

23:20.540 --> 23:23.612
while_some whales can
hear InfrasonIc sounds
as low as seven hertz.

23:23.620 --> 23:25.702
The range
of these frequencies,

23:25.710 --> 23:27.666
they're unlike
anything I've ever seen.

23:27.670 --> 23:29.114
[beeping]

23:30.920 --> 23:35.493
[varying pitches playing]

23:50.830 --> 23:55.164
[sound intensifying]

23:55.170 --> 23:56.535
Ben is in pain?

24:00.120 --> 24:01.371
[hissing]

24:05.040 --> 24:08.578
[loud discordant notes]

24:08.580 --> 24:10.241
[Ryn screaming]

24:11.580 --> 24:13.957
-Stop this!
-[recording stops]

24:13.960 --> 24:16.451
[breathing heavily]

24:19.790 --> 24:23.783
[rock music playing
