24:23.790 --> 24:25.667
[customers conversing]

24:27.830 --> 24:30.037
So, uh,
anything show up?

24:30.040 --> 24:32.497
When they were looking
at your brain, or whatever.

24:32.500 --> 24:34.570
Still running
more tests, but...

24:34.580 --> 24:36.457
everything looks okay.

24:38.460 --> 24:39.449
Good.

24:42.500 --> 24:45.242
This, um, song thing,

24:45.250 --> 24:46.660
what does it do to you?

24:46.670 --> 24:48.319
I mean, besides make you
drink before 5:00

24:48.330 --> 24:50.457
or move to Iowa.

24:50.460 --> 24:51.449
[laughs]

24:51.460 --> 24:53.746
All depends on the person.

24:53.750 --> 24:55.240
I know I feel good.

24:55.250 --> 24:56.820
I think
that's the IPA talking.

24:56.830 --> 24:58.115
[laughs] What?

25:02.420 --> 25:03.876
Wanted to tell you,

25:03.880 --> 25:06.280
I'm glad
you're doing better.

25:07.710 --> 25:09.530
You're a good guy, Xan.

25:09.540 --> 25:11.167
You deserve to be happy.

25:12.210 --> 25:13.279
Thanks.

25:14.960 --> 25:17.781
You know, so do you.

25:17.790 --> 25:19.417
It's good to see
that you're

25:19.420 --> 25:21.206
giving yourself
a break for a change.

25:21.210 --> 25:22.609
You weren't always
the Maddie who felt like

25:22.620 --> 25:24.030
she had to take care
of everyone else.

25:24.040 --> 25:26.031
[laughs]

25:27.710 --> 25:30.417
Not always having
to control everything?

25:30.420 --> 25:32.741
Just doing what feels right
in the moment.

25:32.750 --> 25:35.116
I forgot what it's like.

25:35.120 --> 25:36.826
-Feels good.
-Yeah, I bet.

25:36.830 --> 25:38.457
[laughing] Yeah.

25:38.460 --> 25:39.916
[Siren song echoing]

25:39.920 --> 25:41.785
Whoa. Hey.

25:41.790 --> 25:42.916
What are you doing?

25:47.000 --> 25:48.160
Maddie.

25:49.210 --> 25:50.416
Maddie.

25:50.420 --> 25:51.409
[door opens]

25:52.710 --> 25:54.029
[door closes]

25:55.040 --> 25:57.611
[boat horn blows]

25:59.880 --> 26:02.872
Ryn, remember,
we're pretending

26:02.880 --> 26:05.246
that we're
just friends, okay?

26:05.250 --> 26:07.912
But more than friends.

26:07.920 --> 26:09.911
Ryn lie?

26:09.920 --> 26:11.035
Yeah, kind of.

26:12.710 --> 26:15.873
But this is
for my mom's sake.

26:15.880 --> 26:17.745
You helped her
in the hospital.

26:17.750 --> 26:19.160
She wants to thank you.

26:19.170 --> 26:21.536
She doesn't need
to know any more than that.

26:22.580 --> 26:23.660
Not right now.

26:25.290 --> 26:26.370
Brother!

26:26.380 --> 26:27.779
-Hey, man.
-Hey.

26:30.670 --> 26:31.739
And who might this be?

26:31.750 --> 26:33.320
This is Ryn,

26:33.330 --> 26:35.571
Maddie's exchange student
friend from Finland.

26:37.040 --> 26:38.917
Wait a minute. You_--
You look really famIIIar.

26:40.880 --> 26:41.869
[snaps]

26:41.880 --> 26:43.199
It was a pool party

26:43.210 --> 26:44.370
at the Siren Song Motel
a while back, right?

26:44.380 --> 26:45.699
Yes.

26:47.420 --> 26:48.785
All right.
Well, let me take that.

26:48.790 --> 26:49.916
-Come on inside, guys.
-All right.

26:53.000 --> 26:56.538
I have to admit,
I was surprised
to hear from you.

26:56.540 --> 26:57.780
[laughs]

26:57.790 --> 27:00.998
Much less find myself
sitting in your home.

27:01.000 --> 27:02.615
We're family, Helen.

27:02.620 --> 27:04.827
It threw me for a loop
when I found out,

27:04.830 --> 27:08.414
but I think maybe
it's time we started
acting like it.

27:08.420 --> 27:10.160
I agree.

27:10.170 --> 27:11.956
[soft jazz playing]

27:11.960 --> 27:13.496
-Mom.
-Hey.

27:13.500 --> 27:14.876
You look so good.

27:14.880 --> 27:16.245
[laughs]

27:16.250 --> 27:17.410
I'm so glad
you made it.

27:19.000 --> 27:22.288
I see you brought
my favorite new person.

27:22.290 --> 27:23.780
It's so good
to see you again.

27:23.790 --> 27:25.951
Ryn-- friend from Finland.

27:25.960 --> 27:27.450
How lovely.

27:27.460 --> 27:28.666
Where's Maddie?

27:28.670 --> 27:29.955
She's held up.

27:29.960 --> 27:30.779
She'||-- She'll be here.

27:32.250 --> 27:33.911
Ben.

27:33.920 --> 27:34.818
Dad.

27:37.920 --> 27:39.410
I'm sorry.
I don't think we've met.

27:39.420 --> 27:40.910
I'm Ted, Ben's father.

27:40.920 --> 27:42.990
This is Ryn, Ben's friend.

27:43.000 --> 27:44.615
From Finland.

27:44.620 --> 27:46.827
Oh, wow.
What city you from?

27:46.830 --> 27:48.491
No city.

27:48.500 --> 27:50.206
Mm. A country girl.
I like it.

27:50.210 --> 27:51.450
Yeah.

27:51.460 --> 27:52.870
Well, it's nice
to meet you, Ryn.

27:52.880 --> 27:54.871
You mind ifI steal him
for a second?

27:54.880 --> 27:56.495
Stealing is bad.

27:56.500 --> 27:58.115
[laughter]

27:58.120 --> 28:00.327
It's okay.
I'll be right back.

28:10.040 --> 28:11.951
So I don't know what kind
of strings you pulled,

28:11.960 --> 28:15.532
but, uh,
your mother's recovery
is progressing

28:15.540 --> 28:17.167
extremely well.

28:17.170 --> 28:18.455
She told you.

28:18.460 --> 28:20.826
Yeah. After the fact,
if you ask me.

28:20.830 --> 28:22.240
Why the hell
didn't you tell me?

28:22.250 --> 28:23.615
What were you thinking, huh?

28:23.620 --> 28:25.030
Dad, there was no time.

28:25.040 --> 28:26.450
IfI had told you,

28:26.460 --> 28:28.030
would you have ever
gone along with it?

28:29.880 --> 28:31.780
Look, it was
Mom's choice, Dad.

28:31.790 --> 28:32.950
She made it.

28:34.830 --> 28:36.878
Your mother gets
her mind set on something,

28:39.000 --> 28:40.956
trying to change it
is an exercise in futility.

28:41.960 --> 28:44.611
Yeah.
On that we can agree.

28:45.790 --> 28:49.954
So, you two met
in the hospital?

28:49.960 --> 28:51.029
-Mm-hmm.
-Yes.

28:51.040 --> 28:52.496
I help Ben's mother.

28:52.500 --> 28:53.876
She sure did.

28:53.880 --> 28:55.666
Visited me at my worst.

28:55.670 --> 28:57.035
Alleviated the pain.

28:57.040 --> 28:58.826
How did she do that?

28:58.830 --> 29:01.617
I'm not sure, actually.

29:01.620 --> 29:06.068
She just sort of placed
her hands above me and

29:06.080 --> 29:07.377
sang.

29:08.460 --> 29:09.666
She sang to you?

29:09.670 --> 29:11.490
Not song.

29:11.500 --> 29:15.038
Different sound.
For helping.

29:16.670 --> 29:18.285
Well, whatever it was,
I need to download it,

29:18.290 --> 29:20.451
