possibly swim this deep.

29:33.290 --> 29:34.826
You're the expert.
What do you think?

29:34.830 --> 29:36.741
[drill grinding]

29:39.710 --> 29:41.416
[Ben] Looks
like someone is playing

29:41.420 --> 29:43.206
a very good trick
on Klesco.

29:43.210 --> 29:44.996
What do you mean?

29:45.000 --> 29:48.492
Like you said,
there's no other explanation.

29:48.500 --> 29:50.616
It just makes no sense.

29:52.290 --> 29:54.326
I'm curious, how did
you and Ben become friends?

29:54.330 --> 29:56.912
Ben almost hit me
WIth car.

29:56.920 --> 29:58.205
Um...

29:58.210 --> 29:59.700
Avid bicyclist,
this one.

29:59.710 --> 30:00.916
-Oh.
-[He|en laughs]

30:00.920 --> 30:02.535
Thank God
she had a helmet on, hmm?

30:04.080 --> 30:05.206
How are you guys doing?

30:05.210 --> 30:07.075
Oh, just in time.

30:07.080 --> 30:08.991
I need a drink.

30:10.040 --> 30:11.109
Ryn?

30:12.580 --> 30:13.911
Mom, I know
I already said it,

30:13.920 --> 30:16.992
but, really,
you look so great.

30:17.000 --> 30:20.163
Well, I can't wait to start
feeling even better.

30:20.170 --> 30:22.206
Yeah, slow but steady.

30:22.210 --> 30:23.825
I hope not too slow.

30:23.830 --> 30:25.878
Do you know when I'll
be getting my next dose?

30:27.790 --> 30:30.782
I'm not sure.

30:30.790 --> 30:32.030
I'll talk to the doctor.

30:32.040 --> 30:33.416
Great.

30:35.790 --> 30:37.246
[clink]

