33:10.960 --> 33:12.166
[footsteps]

33:12.170 --> 33:13.455
[Elaine]
Maddie! Oh, you made it.

33:13.460 --> 33:14.996
I'm so glad.

33:15.000 --> 33:17.616
Um, please sit.
You're just in time.

33:17.620 --> 33:20.578
So Sylvia has prepared
her world famous duck roast.

33:20.580 --> 33:22.241
It should be one
for the books.

33:23.290 --> 33:24.279
You okay?

33:24.290 --> 33:25.780
Yeah.

33:30.330 --> 33:32.207
All right.

33:35.250 --> 33:38.287
You've known
Maddie the longest
out of all her friends.

33:39.620 --> 33:42.032
Probably knew her
better than I ever did.

33:43.670 --> 33:47.071
I guess I thought
if anyone can tell me

33:47.080 --> 33:49.412
what's really
going on with her,

33:49.420 --> 33:50.455
it might be you.

33:50.460 --> 33:52.917
[sighs] Well, she's--

33:52.920 --> 33:54.456
She's had
a rough few months.

33:54.460 --> 33:55.870
Yeah.

33:55.880 --> 33:57.245
Lots of work stress.

33:58.580 --> 34:00.241
But you know Maddie.

34:00.250 --> 34:03.242
She's a fighter, yeah?

34:03.250 --> 34:04.706
Whatever's getting her
worked up, don't worry,

34:04.710 --> 34:06.746
she'll bounce back.

34:06.750 --> 34:10.117
I don't mean
to sound closed-minded,

34:10.120 --> 34:13.283
and it's not that _I care
that she's seeIng
more than one person,

34:13.290 --> 34:15.076
man or woman, it's just--

34:15.080 --> 34:17.287
Um... Um, uh...

34:17.290 --> 34:18.746
I'm sor--
What do you mean?

34:18.750 --> 34:21.457
Her being
with Ben and Ryn?

34:22.750 --> 34:23.785
They're...

34:25.380 --> 34:27.610
You know, together.

34:27.620 --> 34:28.700
[laughing]

34:28.710 --> 34:31.110
Come on. No, no, it's--

34:31.120 --> 34:32.417
Ryn's a-- She's--

34:34.330 --> 34:35.615
Wait.

34:36.620 --> 34:40.329
So Ryn and Maddie

34:42.040 --> 34:43.416
and Ben--

34:43.420 --> 34:46.207
